import { createStore, combineReducers, applyMiddleware } from "redux";
import thunk from 'redux-thunk';
import { composeWithDevTools } from 'redux-devtools-extension';

import { AdminChangePasswordReducer, AdminForgotPasswordReducer, AdminResetPasswordReducer, AdminGetProfileReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/AuthReducers';
import { AdminSidebarReducer, AdminSidebarVerticalReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/CommonReducers';
import { AdminDashboardCountReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/DashboardReducers';
import { AdminAddUserReducer, AdminGetUserReducer, AdminGetByIdUserReducer, AdminEditUserReducer, AdminChangeStatusUserReducer, AdminUpdateUserStatusReducer, AdminDeleteUserReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/UserReducers';
import { AdminAddCategoryReducer, AdminGetCategoryReducer, AdminGetParentCategoryReducer, AdminGetChildCategoryReducer, AdminGetByIdCategoryReducer, AdminEditCategoryReducer, AdminChangeStatusCategoryReducer, AdminDeleteCategoryReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/CategoryReducers';
import { AdminAddBannerReducer, AdminGetBannerReducer, AdminGetByIdBannerReducer, AdminEditBannerReducer, AdminChangeStatusBannerReducer, AdminDeleteBannerReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/BannerReducers';
import { AdminAddProductReducer, AdminGetProductReducer, AdminGetByIdProductReducer, AdminEditProductReducer, AdminChangeStatusProductReducer, AdminDeleteProductReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/ProductReducers';
import { AdminAddManufacturerReducer, AdminGetManufacturerReducer, AdminGetActiveManufacturerReducer, AdminGetByIdManufacturerReducer, AdminEditManufacturerReducer, AdminChangeStatusManufacturerReducer, AdminDeleteManufacturerReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/ManufacturerReducers';
import { AdminGetNewsletterReducer, AdminDeleteNewsletterReducer } from './Redux/Reducers/NewsletterReducers';

const reducer = combineReducers({
  AdminChangePasswordState: AdminChangePasswordReducer,
  AdminForgotPasswordState: AdminForgotPasswordReducer,
  AdminResetPasswordState: AdminResetPasswordReducer,
  AdminGetProfileState: AdminGetProfileReducer,

  AdminSidebarState: AdminSidebarReducer,
  AdminSidebarVerticalState: AdminSidebarVerticalReducer,

  AdminDashboardCountState: AdminDashboardCountReducer,

  AdminAddUserState: AdminAddUserReducer,
  AdminGetUserState: AdminGetUserReducer,
  AdminGetByIdUserState: AdminGetByIdUserReducer,
  AdminEditUserState: AdminEditUserReducer,
  AdminChangeStatusUserState: AdminChangeStatusUserReducer,
  AdminUpdateUserStatusState: AdminUpdateUserStatusReducer,
  AdminDeleteUserState: AdminDeleteUserReducer,

  AdminAddCategoryState: AdminAddCategoryReducer,
  AdminGetCategoryState: AdminGetCategoryReducer,
  AdminGetParentCategoryState: AdminGetParentCategoryReducer,
  AdminGetChildCategoryState: AdminGetChildCategoryReducer,
  AdminGetByIdCategoryState: AdminGetByIdCategoryReducer,
  AdminEditCategoryState: AdminEditCategoryReducer,
  AdminChangeStatusCategoryState: AdminChangeStatusCategoryReducer,
  AdminDeleteCategoryState: AdminDeleteCategoryReducer,

  AdminAddBannerState: AdminAddBannerReducer,
  AdminGetBannerState: AdminGetBannerReducer,
  AdminGetByIdBannerState: AdminGetByIdBannerReducer,
  AdminEditBannerState: AdminEditBannerReducer,
  AdminChangeStatusBannerState: AdminChangeStatusBannerReducer,
  AdminDeleteBannerState: AdminDeleteBannerReducer,

  AdminAddProductState: AdminAddProductReducer,
  AdminGetProductState: AdminGetProductReducer,
  AdminGetByIdProductState: AdminGetByIdProductReducer,
  AdminEditProductState: AdminEditProductReducer,
  AdminChangeStatusProductState: AdminChangeStatusProductReducer,
  AdminDeleteProductState: AdminDeleteProductReducer,

  AdminAddManufacturerState: AdminAddManufacturerReducer,
  AdminGetManufacturerState: AdminGetManufacturerReducer,
  AdminGetActiveManufacturerState: AdminGetActiveManufacturerReducer,
  AdminGetByIdManufacturerState: AdminGetByIdManufacturerReducer,
  AdminEditManufacturerState: AdminEditManufacturerReducer,
  AdminChangeStatusManufacturerState: AdminChangeStatusManufacturerReducer,
  AdminDeleteManufacturerState: AdminDeleteManufacturerReducer,
  

  AdminGetNewsletterState: AdminGetNewsletterReducer,
  AdminDeleteNewsletterState: AdminDeleteNewsletterReducer,
  
});

let initialState = {}
const middleware = [thunk]
const store = createStore(reducer, initialState, composeWithDevTools(applyMiddleware(...middleware)))
export default store;
